{"id":515,"date":"2024-08-02T18:36:07","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T18:36:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=515"},"modified":"2024-08-02T18:36:07","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T18:36:07","slug":"tm022-solar-beam","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm022-solar-beam\/","title":{"rendered":"TM022 Solar Beam"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM022 Solar Beam<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found in Magnolia Fields, in the Southeast area that you reach by Surfing. It\u2019s hidden behind some trees.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>A 2-turn move that blasts the foe with absorbed energy in the second turn.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Grass<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Redwood Village<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm01-cut\/\">Cut<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Starting from Redwood Village, head West to exit the village.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-magnolia-village-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Magnolia Village Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Magnolia Village Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue following the path going West after leaving the village.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-going-west-after-leaving-the-village.jpg\" alt=\"Going West after leaving the village. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going West after leaving the village.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After making a straight line West and using Surf to cross the water, you\u2019ll eventually get on land where you want to continue on this path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-landing-on-the-opposite-island.jpg\" alt=\"Landing on the opposite island. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Landing on the opposite island.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The path will be cut off by some trees to your south that you can use Cut on. Use cut to take them down, then start going South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-using-cut-to-get-access-to-the-path-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Using Cut to get access to the path going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Cut to get access to the path going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see some more trees you can use Cut on. <\/p>\n<p>Cut down these trees and follow that path as well.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-using-cut-on-some-trees-to-continue-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Using Cut on some trees to continue going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Cut on some trees to continue going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you can, walk around the trees to your East before continuing on that path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-walking-around-the-trees-to-the-east.jpg\" alt=\"Walking around the trees to the East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking around the trees to the East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll have to use Surf again to continue East.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-leave-the-island-and-go-east.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to leave the island and go East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Surf to leave the island and go East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>First, you\u2019ll land on a rocky island that\u2019s a huge rock.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-landing-on-a-rocky-island-and-continuing-east.jpg\" alt=\"Landing on a rocky island and continuing East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Landing on a rocky island and continuing East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, after using Surf to get off that huge chunk of rock, you\u2019ll land on a proper island where you want to keep going East.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/09-pokemon-unbound-landing-on-another-island-using-surf-to-cross-the-water-.jpg\" alt=\"Landing on another island using Surf to cross the water. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Landing on another island using Surf to cross the water.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When the path East gets cut off, turn North and follow that path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/10-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-north.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path North. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path North.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The TM for Solar Beam is hidden by some trees at the very end of this path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/11-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-solar-beam-at-the-end-of-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Solar Beam at the end of the path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Solar Beam at the end of the path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":516,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-515","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/515","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/516"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=515"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=515"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}